to, com dupla intençăo, convida Camila para jantar em sua casa para que ela possa conhecer a sua nova família. Ezequiel insiste em falar com ela sobre romance e sentimentos e a jovem lembra-lhe que năo foi isso que combinaram. Marcelina visita Ezequiel no hospital e ele aproveita para ameaçá-la se ela tentar magoar Camila novamente." type="episode" contentRating="NONADULT" duration="3214000" grandparentArt="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/272_1672724.jpg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/687fff08c082969749e5c0d6" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/687fff08c082969749e5c0d6" grandparentRatingKey="687fff08c082969749e5c0d6" grandparentThumb="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/wedotv_amor_piel_salvaje20282_1672496-portrait.jpg" grandparentTitle="Piel Salvaje" grandparentType="show" index="73" parentIndex="1" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/272_1672724.jpg" title="S01E073" userState="0"><Image alt="S01E073" type="coverArt" url="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/272_1672724.jpg"/><Image alt="S01E073" type="coverPoster" url="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/wedotv_amor_piel_salvaje20282_1672496-portrait.jpg"/><Image alt="S01E073" type="snapshot" url="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/272_1672724.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" id="6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" ratingKey="genre_6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" slug="drama" tag="Drama" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1774328210" duration="3790000" endsAt="1774332000" id="69b9495ec2e967105c781d7d" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1774347756" duration="3214000" endsAt="1774350970" id="69b9495ec2e967105c781d83" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1774369800" duration="3214000" endsAt="177